snippet.title: Best VGM 2430 - Mighty Morphin Power Rangers : The Fighting Edition - Data Zone
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
Mighty Morphin Power Rangers: The Fighting Edition (1995)
Data Zone
Hiroyuki Iwatsuki
